{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":793,"text":"We humans are becoming an urban species,"},{"time":6360,"text":"so cities, they are our natural habitat."},{"time":10160,"text":"That is where we live."},{"time":12720,"text":"In 2014, over 54 percent"},{"time":17000,"text":"of the world population"},{"time":18640,"text":"was living in cities,"},{"time":22120,"text":"and I can bet you"},{"time":24280,"text":"that so many of these people have thought"},{"time":26960,"text":"of how they would do things differently,"},{"time":29560,"text":"like if I only had the tools"},{"time":32240,"text":"to change things in my city,"},{"time":35640,"text":"what would I do?"},{"time":36920,"text":"What would my dream city be like?"},{"time":40360,"text":"And these tools,"},{"time":41920,"text":"this is just what we gave them."},{"time":46120,"text":"Two years ago, my team and I,"},{"time":48680,"text":"we released a game,"},{"time":50120,"text":"\"Cities: Skylines.\""},{"time":51840,"text":"It is a game about building cities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55680,"text":"So I have always been\ninterested in cities as systems."},{"time":59360,"text":"It's something that I find\nimmensely interesting."},{"time":63280,"text":"But what I didn't understand"},{"time":65440,"text":"was that I am not alone in this."},{"time":68800,"text":"People love cities."},{"time":70360,"text":"They are interested. They have ideas."},{"time":72880,"text":"The game was an instant hit."},{"time":75120,"text":"So far, over three and a half\nmillion people have played it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81280,"text":"And it's not just about playing."},{"time":84080,"text":"We also have really awesome\nsharing systems."},{"time":88840,"text":"So people play, they create cities"},{"time":91560,"text":"and then they are sharing these creations,"},{"time":94400,"text":"showing off what they have made."},{"time":97400,"text":"And what I will show you"},{"time":100560,"text":"is some of these cities"},{"time":102800,"text":"created by the players."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104720,"text":"So the game is about self-expression,"},{"time":109240,"text":"creativity,"},{"time":110520,"text":"not just overcoming the challenges\nposed by the simulation."},{"time":115160,"text":"It is about showing\nwhat your cities look like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120480,"text":"So I have a couple of videos."},{"time":122600,"text":"These are from YouTube."},{"time":124440,"text":"And these are some of the most\ninteresting city designs I have seen."},{"time":128919,"text":"So they are all different,"},{"time":130440,"text":"and I hope you like all of these."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135040,"text":"This one is called The Netherlands."},{"time":137400,"text":"It's by Silvarret."},{"time":139360,"text":"And when you start the game,"},{"time":141520,"text":"you have an empty piece of land."},{"time":144160,"text":"This land, it can be based\non the real world,"},{"time":148080,"text":"it can be hand-crafted in the map editor,"},{"time":151040,"text":"or you can, of course, download\na city made by someone else"},{"time":154040,"text":"and play in that."},{"time":155600,"text":"But what Silvarret has done here"},{"time":158040,"text":"is that what he wanted to make"},{"time":160640,"text":"was not a real city."},{"time":163400,"text":"This is a fantasy city,"},{"time":165080,"text":"even though it looks real."},{"time":166800,"text":"So what he wanted to do was a fantasy city\nthat could be in the Netherlands."},{"time":172320,"text":"So he kind of investigated"},{"time":174680,"text":"what are the characteristics\nof cities in the Netherlands"},{"time":178720,"text":"and combined a couple of those,"},{"time":181320,"text":"and this is what he created."},{"time":184040,"text":"So it is a city,"},{"time":185720,"text":"but it is not a real city,"},{"time":188000,"text":"but it could be."},{"time":189280,"text":"It looks just like the Netherlands."},{"time":191560,"text":"So the places are really\ndensely populated."},{"time":194960,"text":"So what you need is highways, trains,"},{"time":199960,"text":"anything connecting\nthese small town centers together."},{"time":204240,"text":"Lots of people, lots of moving,"},{"time":206480,"text":"so transportation is the key here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210760,"text":"But then let's go even more\non the fantasy side."},{"time":214240,"text":"Let's go into the future."},{"time":218280,"text":"This is one of my personal favorites."},{"time":220640,"text":"These city designs\nare what I love the most."},{"time":225000,"text":"So this is a tiered city by Conflictnerd,"},{"time":228320,"text":"and the basic idea is\nthat you have concentric circle routes."},{"time":234240,"text":"So the city is a big circle"},{"time":236560,"text":"with tinier circles inside."},{"time":239400,"text":"And the thing is that you put\nall of the services in the center,"},{"time":243680,"text":"and then people actually live\non the outer ring,"},{"time":247120,"text":"because there is less traffic,\nless noise, less pollution,"},{"time":250920,"text":"so that is where you want to live."},{"time":252880,"text":"But the services\nare still really close by."},{"time":255840,"text":"They are in the center."},{"time":257519,"text":"And this is the soul of the game."},{"time":261360,"text":"The player has to understand"},{"time":263400,"text":"what are the wishes, what are the needs"},{"time":266000,"text":"of the tiny people living in the cities."},{"time":269680,"text":"So you need to know\nwhere you should put the things."},{"time":273520,"text":"Like, it's not enough to have a hospital."},{"time":276080,"text":"It needs to be accessible."},{"time":277840,"text":"Citizens need to reach the hospital."},{"time":280960,"text":"And this is one way to do it."},{"time":285200,"text":"So maybe this is something\nthat we might be seeing someday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290200,"text":"And then even more into the future."},{"time":294280,"text":"Astergea by Yuttho."},{"time":296840,"text":"So Yuttho does YouTube videos\nand plays the game."},{"time":300640,"text":"What he did here\nwas actually a 12-point series"},{"time":305320,"text":"of creating this city."},{"time":308000,"text":"So what he does is he plays the game,"},{"time":310560,"text":"he records it"},{"time":311840,"text":"and he explains as he's going\nwhat he's doing and why."},{"time":316160,"text":"And as a part of this series,"},{"time":318320,"text":"he actually did an interview\nwith an actual urban planner"},{"time":321600,"text":"called Jeff Speck."},{"time":323960,"text":"And Speck is an expert\non the concept of walkability."},{"time":328280,"text":"The basic idea is that\nif you want your citizens to walk,"},{"time":332680,"text":"which is kind of beneficial,"},{"time":334640,"text":"you actually need to have walking\nas a reasonable means of transportation."},{"time":340400,"text":"It should be a good way to reach places."},{"time":343760,"text":"So what Yuttho did\nwas that he explained this concept,"},{"time":347400,"text":"he had Speck explain it, too,"},{"time":349440,"text":"and then he applied it\nto the city that he was building."},{"time":353200,"text":"So what we are seeing\nis Yuttho's vision of the future:"},{"time":358120,"text":"lots of public transportation,\nwalkways, plazas,"},{"time":362400,"text":"connecting high-rise buildings."},{"time":364800,"text":"Maybe this is what\nthe future might look like."},{"time":368400,"text":"And the game system\nworks really well for this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371880,"text":"We are seeing some\nreal-world uses to this game."},{"time":376720,"text":"So we know that some urban planners\nare using it as a sketching tool,"},{"time":381440,"text":"so while the simulation\nis not completely realistic,"},{"time":385760,"text":"it is realistic enough\nthat if something works in the game,"},{"time":389720,"text":"it is highly likely that it\nwill also work in the real world,"},{"time":394640,"text":"so that you can actually try out things,"},{"time":396760,"text":"see if this intersection\nmight fit this kind of a situation."},{"time":401760,"text":"If we build a new road, would it help?"},{"time":405320,"text":"And this is what you can do\nwith this game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409080,"text":"There was one really\ninteresting contest held"},{"time":412200,"text":"by the Finnish city of HÃ¤meenlinna."},{"time":415440,"text":"So what they did\nwas that they had a new area"},{"time":417680,"text":"that they wanted to develop in the city."},{"time":420960,"text":"They made a map with the existing city,"},{"time":423520,"text":"they left empty the area\nthat they would want to develop"},{"time":426720,"text":"and shared this map."},{"time":429080,"text":"So anyone could download the map,"},{"time":432120,"text":"play the game, build the area"},{"time":433760,"text":"and submit their creations\nto the city council."},{"time":438280,"text":"So they have not yet built anything,"},{"time":440920,"text":"but it might just be\nthat they use one of these plans"},{"time":444720,"text":"made with the game"},{"time":447080,"text":"to actually build the real city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452080,"text":"And these videos that I have shown you,"},{"time":454800,"text":"these are the people who are\ncoming up with new kinds of solutions."},{"time":460000,"text":"We know that cities are growing."},{"time":461880,"text":"They're getting bigger as we go,"},{"time":464360,"text":"and the percentage of population\nliving in cities is projected to rise."},{"time":470600,"text":"So we need the solutions"},{"time":472520,"text":"and these people, playing the game,"},{"time":475240,"text":"they are trying out\ndifferent kinds of solutions."},{"time":477920,"text":"They might have something\nthat is really important."},{"time":482640,"text":"So what we are seeing here is dream cities\nthat might be real one day."},{"time":490400,"text":"So it might be"},{"time":492000,"text":"that this is not just a game."},{"time":496000,"text":"It might be a way"},{"time":498680,"text":"to decide our own fate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501920,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503160,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}